        <strong>A large widget</strong> in the posting flow to draw attention to
        the camera.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>A guide with basic tips</strong> on how to prepare for shooting.
      </li>
      <li><strong>Object recognition</strong> and subcategory refinement.</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Autofocus, centering assistance</strong>, and different formats
